{"ec":"ET00004346","t":"Housefull","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/et00004346.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/et00004346.jpg","d":"`Housefull` is a romantic comedy entertainer which narrates the story of Aarush - the world`s unluckiest man. Being jinxed he believes his bad luck can vanish if he finds true love. In this quest for true love how one lie leads to another and how different people from different walks of life come together adding even more confusion to this hilarious comedy of errors resulting in total chaos and mayhem. As Deepika tells Akshay in the film `Jis jhooth se kissi ka ghar basta ho, voh jhooth jhooth nahin hota``.","rd":"2010-04-30","rt":155,"ct":"UA","g":["Comedy"],"l":["Hindi"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Akshay Kumar","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/akshay-kumar-94-1681713982.jpg"],["Lara Dutta","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/lara-dutta-1256-19-09-2017-04-53-26.jpg"],["Malaika Arora","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/malaika-arora-1057424-24-03-2017-12-45-10.jpg"],["Arjun Rampal","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/arjun-rampal-225-24-03-2017-12-44-48.jpg"],["Riteish Deshmukh","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/riteish-deshmukh-25378-13-09-2017-04-40-50.jpg"],["Deepika Padukone","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/deepika-padukone-2822-12-09-2017-06-31-43.jpg"],["Daisy Irani","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/daisy-irani-491-13-08-2018-04-53-20.jpg"],["Randhir Kapoor","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/randhir-kapoor-16529-24-03-2017-17-59-42.jpg"],["Jiah Khan","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/jiah-khan-5712-20-11-2017-04-49-16