{"ec":"ET00004461","t":"Badmaash Company","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/et00004461.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/et00004461.jpg","d":"Life in the 1990`s was remarkably different for the average Indian. Consumerism had not set in. It was devoid of most of the luxuries of the West. In fact everything ``imported`` was good, and everything Indian, pass. Badmaash Company is an extraordinary story set in the 1990`s in middle class Bombay (as it was known then), of four ordinary youngsters Karan (Shahid Kapoor), Bulbul (Anushka Sharma), Chandu (Vir Das) and Zing (Meiyang Chang) who came together to start an import business of things longed for by yuppie Indians! What made their venture such a stupendous success was the fact that they found a way to beat the system and soon became the undisputed kings in their business, realising their one dream of making quick money by doing all the wrong things - the right way!","rd":"2010-05-07","rt":144,"ct":"UA","g":["Comedy","Crime","Drama"],"l":["Hindi"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Anushka Sharma","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/anushka-sharma-7978-13-09-2017-04-37-40.jpg"],["Shahid Kapoor","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/shahid-kapoor-2094-1680754317.jpg"],["Vir Das","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/vir-das-3049-1757992801.jpg"],["Meiyang Chang","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/meiyang-chang-16792-24-03-2017-17-55-24.jpg"],["Anupam Kher","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/anupam-kher-211-09-10-2017-04-27-29.jpg"],["Pavan Malhotra","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/pavan-malhotra-1675-24-03-2017-18-02-03.jpg"],["Jameel Khan","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/jameel-khan-30358-24-03